===Etymology===
from French [[crétin]], from Vulgar Latin *[[christianus|christia-nus]], from Latin [[Christianus|Chri-stia-nus]], in the lost sense of 'unfortunate person' <!-- what an interesting etymology -->

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A person who fails to develop mentally and physically due to a [[congenital]] deficiency of [[thyroid]] [[hormone]]s.
# {{pejorative}} An [[idiot]].

